sourcesContent: import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { FormControl, FormGroup } from '@angular/forms'; import { SearchParameters } from '../../../entity/SearchParameters'; import { SearchService } from '../../../service/search.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-home', templateUrl: './home.component.html', styleUrls: ['./home.component.scss'] }) export class HomeComponent { constructor(private searchService: SearchService) { } ngOnInit() { this.searchForm = new FormGroup({ type: new FormControl(""), query: new FormControl(""), country: new FormControl(""), locale: new FormControl(""), autocorrect: new FormControl(""), page: new FormControl("") }); } public searchForm!: FormGroup; public GetRequestValue() { let searchParameters: SearchParameters = { q: this.searchForm.value.query, gl: this.searchForm.value.country, hl: this.searchForm.value.locale, autocorrect: this.searchForm.value.autocorrect, page: this.searchForm.value.page, type: this.searchForm.value.type }; } }
